    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Droned is a small project by a single dev to revive some old school action. Compete in AI league, take on the trials or battle it out in arena with your friends. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game reward progression by collecting new drones, weapons &amp; utilities  that compliments your play style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AI LEAGUE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your ultimate drone team and take on AI-controlled squads based on real player loadouts. Climb the leaderboard and defend your rank in this solo competitive mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/6de7a8584aff9d45dbbbb6f88d3fcd7c.poster.avif?t=1753979823\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/6de7a8584aff9d45dbbbb6f88d3fcd7c.webm?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/6de7a8584aff9d45dbbbb6f88d3fcd7c.mp4?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TRIALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A high intense co-op mode—a gauntlet of brutal combat scenarios designed to push your tactical mastery to the edge. Bring your best drone, a trusted ally, and a high-level Codex if you hope to survive. Do you have what it takes to conquer them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/41dc2fc72cd2867d6e86a3db4570e894.poster.avif?t=1753979823\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/41dc2fc72cd2867d6e86a3db4570e894.webm?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/41dc2fc72cd2867d6e86a3db4570e894.mp4?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ARENA</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in intense Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch modes against real players or bots in fast-paced, high-stakes combat. Victory goes to the last drone standing—or the team with the sharpest tactics and deadliest aim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/938e3c5e93a66f722fdcd323537746b0.poster.avif?t=1753979823\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/938e3c5e93a66f722fdcd323537746b0.webm?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/938e3c5e93a66f722fdcd323537746b0.mp4?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZATION AND LOADOUT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your drones with a growing collection of weapons &amp; utilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/e22b31210bd00b68c7e443d40f60b91a.poster.avif?t=1753979823\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/e22b31210bd00b68c7e443d40f60b91a.webm?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712720/extras/e22b31210bd00b68c7e443d40f60b91a.mp4?t=1753979823\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
